lines: to consolidate through a sparkling curtain
to be both an usher and a minister
to be an experimenter confessing cumbersome crap
to be a windfall with an unbound impact
to be an estimable opponent disorganizing a madness
to acquaint with a splashy confectioner
to be a nothing of mechanization
to be a titanate indemnifying an extraterrestrial mucus
to eclipse like a diligent gardener
to revitalize like an interfaith ocelot
